From: Tony Lindgren <tony@atomide.com>
Date: Wed, 17 May 2023 12:52:53 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] ARM: dts: Unify pinctrl-single pin group nodes for omap4
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 6.1.56
Git-commit: 7fff6f6d6e198ad619fea9dbbe9731999af56070

[ Upstream commit 7fff6f6d6e198ad619fea9dbbe9731999af56070 ]

